      -              "unti) !   "         to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
           go to     acc-ind-eml-100.
       acc-ind-eml-490.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Che non contenga spazi                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test                                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-ind-eml        to   w-all-str-alf          .
           move      80                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           perform   all-str-ble-000      thru all-str-ble-999        .
           if        w-all-str-flg        =    spaces
                     go to acc-ind-eml-600.
